thread.title: W Seidl
thread.title_full: Del City reviewed by W Seidl

author: W Seidl
title: W Seidl
text:
The ordered product was delivered quickly, at a great price. The website made it effortless to find exactly what we sought, and ordering was quickly accomplished without confusion. The product, when delivered, was packaged securely and arrived in excellent condition.
We will definitely order from Del City again, and have added them to our internal resource list for future reference. This one is a winner!
